><div class="t m1cd x4a h2d y155b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m844 x29 h2d yfad ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What befell one of the heads of </div><div class="t m124 x27 h2d y8ec ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this nondescript beast? How is the </div><div class="t mbe2 x11 h2d y8ae ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beast regarded by the people of the </div><div class="t m82b x11 h2d y4fc ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">world? Rev. 13:3, 4. </div><div class="t m993 x26 h4 yf79 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NoTE.—&quot;The infliction of the deadly </div><div class="t m553 x11 h4 yd56 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wound points to the downfall of the pa-</div><div class="t m836 x11 h4 y4e1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pacy in 1798.&quot;--The </div><div class="t m343 x9b h30 y4e1 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Great Controversy, </div><div class="t m6c0 x11 h4 y3d1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 579. Along the intervening years that </div><div class="t m3e8 x27 h4 y1321 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wound has been gradually healing, until at </div><div class="t m605 x27 h4 y1976 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the present time the power and prestige of </div><div class="t m249 x11 h4 y85d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Church of Rome is universally appar-</div><div class="t m105c x11 h4 y56c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ent. </div><div class="t m1d0 x4a h2d y1012 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t mc48 x29 h2d y59c ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In what way does , the two-</div><div class="t m6e9 x11 h2d yaad ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">horned beast follow the course of its </div><div class="t mab0 x11 h2d y3d7 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">predecessor? Define the term, &quot;an </div><div class="t m1168 x11 h2d yaf0 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">image to the beast.&quot; Rev. 13:14. </div><div class="t mf4e x26 h4 y988 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NoTE.—&quot;The &apos;image to the beast&apos; repre-</div><div class="t ma60 x11 h4 y1014 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sents that form of apostate Protestantism </div><div class="t 