n of the serpent </div><div class="t m16d x56 h4 y132c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to Eve in Eden,—&quot;Ye shall not surely die,&apos; </div><div class="t m1e2 x56 h4 y93f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">—was the first sermon ever preached upon </div><div class="t mb10 x56 h4 y628 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the immortality of the soul. Yet this decla-</div><div class="t m791 x56 h4 y4bc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ration, resting solely upon the authority of </div><div class="t m69b x56 h4 yfee ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Satan, is echoed from the pulpits of Chris- </div><div class="t m6b0 x90 h36 y45a ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 31 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
